long_description:
SG CAR WASHING EQUIPMENT.

  •    - Pre-soak application system;
  •    - LED Lava System;
  •    - Crystal Waxing System;
  •    - Built-in drying system.
  • 2. Power Supply: 3 PH, 380 V, 50 Hz.
  • 3. Pump Station: WH10120 Taiwan Wuli water pump+15KW Siemens motor (or PF36 water pump+18.5KW Siemens Motor).
  • 4. Drying System: 20.5KW (3x5.5 KW, 1x4 KW Siemens Motors).
